{"name":"教程","postlist":[{"title":"VsCode配置C++","slug":"VsCode配置C","date":"2021-10-09T06:44:23.000Z","updated":"2021-10-10T15:14:36.070Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/VsCode配置C.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jerryc127/CDN@latest/cover/default_bg.png","content":"","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"VsCode","path":"api/tags/VsCode.json"},{"name":"C","path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"教程","path":"api/tags/教程.json"}]},{"title":"Windows10网络感叹号修复","slug":"Windows10网络感叹号修复","date":"2021-10-11T08:27:19.000Z","updated":"2021-10-11T08:54:36.411Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows10网络感叹号修复.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://asuhe.jp/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15DCCAAA4C320A387B32696BA0D9229B.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Windows10-修复网络感叹号bug\"><a href=\"#Windows10-修复网络感叹号bug\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Windows10 修复网络感叹号bug\"></a>Windows10 修复网络感叹号bug</h1><blockquote>\n<p>修复连接显示无internet但是有网的bug，链接在下方</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211011162902502.png\" alt=\"image-20211011162902502\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>打开这个工具，点击一键修复，然后重启就好了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211011163154911.png\" alt=\"image-20211011163154911\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211011163441976.png\" alt=\"image-20211011163441976\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）\"><a href=\"#windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）\"></a><a href=\"https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/BcyXmzrxPWo\">windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）</a></h2><h2 id=\"蓝奏云链接\"><a href=\"#蓝奏云链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"蓝奏云链接\"></a><a href=\"https://syakj.lanzoui.com/irCHJv7sfxe\">蓝奏云链接</a></h2>","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/tags/教程.json"},{"name":"windows10","path":"api/tags/windows10.json"}]},{"title":"Windows远程桌面docker容器","slug":"Windows远程桌面Linux","date":"2021-10-10T07:23:42.000Z","updated":"2021-10-14T12:27:26.195Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows远程桌面Linux.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jerryc127/CDN@latest/cover/default_bg.png","content":"<p>编写Dockerfile文件（可选择dokcer文件，我没测试）</p>\n<p>（Windows无法连通docker容器所以这是Linux中做的实验）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">FROM centos</span><br><span class=\"line\">MAINTAINER Wans&lt;wa.ns@qq.com&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">ENV MYPATH /sbin/init</span><br><span class=\"line\">WORKDIR $MYPATH</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN yum -y install vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN yum -y install net-tools</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN rpm -Uvh https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN yum -y install xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN systemctl start xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN systemctl enable xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">CMD echo $MYPATH</span><br><span class=\"line\">CMD echo &quot;----end----&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>1、放行3389端口，重启防火墙</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --permanent --zone=public --add-port=3389/tcp</span><br><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2、运行docker centos容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -it -p 3389:3389 -p 3350:3350 --privileged true --name mycentos centos /sbin/init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>3、安装xrdp、vim、net-tools</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum -y install vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum -y install net-tools</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -Uvh https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum -y install xrdp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>启动xrdp</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl start xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl enable xrdp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>打开Windows远程连接就好</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211010160758852.png\" alt=\"image-20211010160758852\"></p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}]}]}